Osborne Says Euro Region Needs to End Speculation Over Greece

-- B y   G o n z a l o   V i n a
-- 
2011-10-03T11:17:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/osborne-says-euro-region-needs-to-end-speculation-over-greece.html
Chancellor of the Exchequer  George
Osborne  reiterated calls for European governments to agree on
measures to support  Greece  and stick to that plan. He was
speaking at this  Conservative party ’s annual conference in
Manchester,  England , today.  “The euro zone needs to end all the speculation and decide
what it is going to do with Greece and stick with that
decision,” Osborne said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gonzalo Vina in London at 
